          <div class="flower-row r1">🌷&thinsp;🪷&thinsp;🌷</div>
          <div class="flower-row r2">🌸&thinsp;🌺&thinsp;🌷&thinsp;🌺&thinsp;🌸</div>
          <div class="flower-row r3">🌸&thinsp;🌷&thinsp;🌸&thinsp;🌷&thinsp;🌸</div>
